OnlyRootFilesystem: true (emptyDir for /tmp + spark work dirs),\n   capabilities.drop: [ALL], seccompProfile.type: RuntimeDefault.\nC3 [RBAC/F2] Reconcile Role to declared manifest: remove out-of-band \"pods\" and\n   trim write verbs (delete/update/patch) not needed by the SparkPi batch job;\n   re-apply from version control to stop drift.\nC4 [Network/F3] Add default-deny NetworkPolicy + explicit allows for\n   worker->master 7077 and operator access to UI 8080/8081.\nC5 [Hygiene] Set automountServiceAccountToken: false where the token is not\n   needed; confirm unused \"default\" SA stays unused.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Order of Execution (lowest-risk first)\n\n1. C4 NetworkPolicy (additive; apply default-deny last) — validate connectivity.\n2. C3 RBAC reconcile — confirm Job still runs under reduced permissions.\n3. C2 securityContext hardening — rolling restart of master/worker.\n4. C1 image upgrade — rolling update master/worker, then re-run Job.\n5. C5 SA token hygiene — final tightening.\n\nRationale: apply isolation and least-privilege before the version bump so the\nupgrade is validated against the hardened baseline; keep the version change last\nand easiest to roll back.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Verification Per Step\n\n- C4: kubectl get netpol -n spark-pi; worker logs show registration to\n  spark://spark-master:7077; master 8080 UI reachable only from allowed source.\n- C3: kubectl auth can-i --as=system:serviceaccount:spark-pi:spark-pi <verb> <res>\n  -n spark-pi matches intended matrix; re-run Job -> Completed.\n- C2: kubectl get pod -o jsonpath shows runAsNonRoot/dropped caps; pods Running 1/1;\n  no CrashLoop.\n- C1: kubectl get deploy -o jsonpath='{..image}' shows new digest; kubectl rollout\n  status deploy/spark-master deploy/spark-worker -n spark-pi; re-run spark-pi Job,\n  expect log \"Pi is roughly 3.14...\" and exit 0.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Rollback\n\nEach change applied from version-controlled manifests; rollback = kubectl rollout\nundo (deployments) or re-apply previous manifest (Role, NetworkPolicy, Job). Take a\nkubectl get all,role,rolebinding,netpol -o yaml snapshot before the window.\nbackoffLimit=0 means a failed verification Job run must be deleted and re-created,\nnot auto-retried.\n\n---\n\n## 6. Approval\n\nThis plan must be reviewed and signed off before any kubectl apply is executed.\nNo item above has been applied; the live spark-pi namespace remains exactly as\ninspected on 2026-06-18.\nPLANEOF\nwc -l /tmp/plan.md","description":"Write plan to file"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2144,"cache_read_input_tokens":36114,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2144},"output_tokens":45,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3d47fc9f-97df-4e30-9a3f-a3c5be912fab","uuid":"12383c4a-1475-42d7-a9fc-71c4b2b97353","request_id":"req_011CcAWyiuq5kBWZpa696y7D"}
